(c) cause the contractor to refund the cost of the uninstalled signboards/billboards; and (d) ask the cooperation of the Punong Barangay of Barangay Alibog in resolving conflicts among residents of the two Sitios to effectively benefit the end users of the SALINTUBIG project.

