BAC to: (i) invite, in addition to the representative of the COA, at least two observers in all stages of the procurement process, namely: the Pre-Bid Conference, Bid Opening and Post-qualification phase, pursuant to Section 13.1 of the 2016 Revised IRR of RA No. 9184; (ii) post in the PhilGEPS and in any conspicuous places within the premises of the LGU copies of the Notices of Award, Approved Contracts and Notices to Proceed within the prescribed period pursuant to Sections 37.1.6 and 37.4.2 of the 2016 Revised IRR of RA No. 9184; and (iii) be vigilant in all stages of the procurement process particularly during the bid evaluation and post-qualification phase for proper evaluation and assessment of the eligibility, legal, technical and financial capacities of the prospective bidders;

